Name: Dark Council
Description: Provide Whisperer and Redeemer Upgrade Plan.

Root.Tooltip:
Significantly enhance Whisperer's combat ability.
Choose one from three following upgrades:
1. Split Particle: Allow Whisperer to attack one additional unit.
2. Heavy Particle: Increase range and damage and additional damage versus armored unit of Whisperer's basic attack.
3. High-Speed Particle: Increase Whisperer's attack speed.
Root.Name: Whisperer Advanced Ability Module

Root.Tooltip:
Further improve Whisperer's special ability.
Choose one from three following upgrades:
1. Phase Accumulator: Enable Whisperer to store three blink charge.
2. Phase Displacement: Increases the flash distance of Whisperer by 100%.
3. Phase Reactor: Causes Whisperer to instantly restore 100 shields while Blink.
Root.Name: Whisperer Improved Ability Module

Root.Tooltip:
Unlock Whisperer's basic combat abilities.
These include:
1. Electron Charge: Increase attack range of Shadow Scout by 2
2. Plasma Blast: Unlock Plasma Shock Wave.
Root.Name: Whisperer Basic Ability Module

Root.Tooltip:
Significantly enhance Redeemer's combat ability.
Choose one from three following upgrades:
1. Shadow Chrono: Reduces the cooldown of Dark Entangling by 50%.
2. Shadow Shield: Reduced the cooldown of Shield Storage by 3 seconds.
3. Shadow Dash: Redeemer's Sprint has almost no cooldown.
Root.Name: Redeemer Advanced Ability Module

Root.Tooltip:
Further improve Redeemer's special ability.
Choose one from three following upgrades:
1. Shield Profusion: Increase Redeemer's shield maximum by 100.
2. Armor Profusion: Increase Redeemer's shield armor and health armor by 4.
3. Health Profusion: Redeemer can regenerate health continuously without being interrupted.
Root.Name: Redeemer Improved Ability Module

Root.Tooltip:
Unlock Redeemer's basic combat abilities.
These include:
1. Dark Entangling: Redeemer can stun nearby enemy units.
2. Shield Storage: Redeemer can fully regenerate his shield.
Root.Name: Redeemer Basic Ability Module
